&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/clockwork_ultraviolence_wallpaper.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/clockwork_ultraviolence_wallpaper_sm.jpg" alt="CD cover I created awhile ago, but revised recently © Joshua Keyes 2008 all rights reserved">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/clockwork_ultraviolence_cd.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/clockwork_ultraviolence_cd.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Surf the splash screen</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/surf-the-splash-screen/</link><pubDate>Wed, 30 Jul 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/surf-the-splash-screen/</guid><description>&lt;p>Recently I created a web asset for a college health department web layout.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/portal_beach.jpg">&lt;img src="https://RaihnForge.github.io/images/recovered/portal_beach_sm.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Motorcycle poster for my now famous Dad - A learning project</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/motorcycle-poster-for-my-now-famous-dad-a-learning-project/</link><pubDate>Sun, 27 Jul 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/motorcycle-poster-for-my-now-famous-dad-a-learning-project/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/ducati_poster_dad.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/ducati_poster_dad_sm.jpg" alt="Motorcylce poster for my now famous Dad">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;h5>&lt;/h5>
&lt;p>The original design was from a poster brought from my Dad&amp;rsquo;s trip to Moto GP a couple of weeks ago. The poster concept and design belongs to Yamaha. The photograph was taken of my Dad riding his Ducati during his Zoom Zoom track day at Reno-Fernley Raceway.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>We thought it would be fun to make a parody poster for of him using the same style as the Yamaha poster. I replaced the logos with things that relate to my Dad, military unit crests, friends business, and products that he likes to use, as well as the Reno-Fernley Raceway logo.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Web Design Practice - usord</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/web-design-practice-usord/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Jul 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/web-design-practice-usord/</guid><description>&lt;p>Inspired by the Business card I created, I decided to do a practice web redesign of US Ordnance Inc.&amp;rsquo;s website. Feel free to check it out. Click to enlarge images.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Basic Template&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/misc/web_usord_basic.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/misc/web_usord_basic_th.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Content - About US - Company Overview&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/misc/web_usord_about_us.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/misc/web_usord_about_us_th.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/misc/web_usord_about_us_th.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Business Card Ordance</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/business-card-ordance/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Jun 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/business-card-ordance/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/misc/businesscard_usord_john_doe_small.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>The first art project I did today was a business card.  It is fun to do little business cards because they are micro designs, but the designs could be used to create whole websites!&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Logo Created for Clifford Dunn Music</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/logo-created-for-clifford-dunn-music/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Jun 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/logo-created-for-clifford-dunn-music/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/images/weblayout_cliffconcept_logo.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Web Layout Concept for Clifford Dunn Music</title><link>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/web-layout-concept-for-clifford-dunn-music/</link><pubDate>Mon, 09 Jun 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://RaihnForge.github.io/art/branding/web-layout-concept-for-clifford-dunn-music/</guid><description>&lt;p>Click to see larger versions of each graphic.&lt;/p>
