&lt;p>Header for MemberChat.net&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;a href="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/design/memberchat_banner.jpg">&lt;img src="http://www.joshuakeyes.us/raihn/art/design/memberchat_banner.jpg" alt="">&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
